==English==
===Etymology===
1.) Tracing a language back to its roots and deciding breaking it into it's most simple form.

2.) A branch of linguistics.

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /stə'kɑ:nəvʌɪt/

===Noun===
{{en-noun|Stakhanovite|Stakhanovites}}
